                <h1>Choosing the Perfect Headshot Background Color</h1>
                <p>When choosing a background color for your headshot, consider its impact on perception. Soft colors like light blue or gray convey approachability, while bold colors like dark red or green can suggest confidence. Ensure the color complements your outfit, enhances your features, and aligns with your personal brand for maximum effect.</p>
